{"tid":898944,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"\"傳奇嘉賓\"...TWICE,以完整體出演《Running Man》","createTime":"2018-11-12T05:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T00:39:59.000Z","uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c368154660aa68dc6dcbcd86502b08654066220","tid":898944,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:04:13.000Z","msg":"Twice將登上《Running Man》. 期間每次出演時都會製作傳奇節目,展現良好的合作,再加上此次是完全體的出演,因此更加令人期待.<br />\n<br />\n12日,據影視界透露,TWICE當天將進行SBS招牌綜藝節目《Running Man》的錄製. 計劃以完整體參與錄製,與《running man》成員展開比賽. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RLZVz3u.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRLZVz3u.gif&h=891ec148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n架架古古<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好分開兩集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想睇多賢跳鷹舞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83456d41edac651d365b783d6d7db3a396b7475","tid":898944,"uid":45847,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgkBjyK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgkBjyK.jpg&h=725b74fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我愛多腎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多腎愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4167d7f4ab0e9aa2d4eecbc190814360b1997f7","tid":898944,"uid":185377,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a83456d41edac651d365b783d6d7db3a396b7475","tid":898944,"uid":45847,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05